column6:
N3tSensors AGRO PLUS is the Premium version of N3tSensors AGRO.
The establish partnership between NumbersAgain and Itri Corporation (owner of Hawk-Eye™ Systems) gave us the possibility to expand our scope and advantages.
The N3tSensors AGRO PLUS Platform gives you the power to have:
 - 24/7/365 Real-Time Monitoring and Control;
 - Measurement & Listening to what the Crop has to "Say";
 - Prescribing Irrigation;
 - Remote Scouting Crop; 
 - Integration of new and existing Sensors and Agricultural Systems;
 - Dashboard in a Web Browser (no App needed);
 - Alarms by Email, SMS and Voice;
 - Data Export.
N3tSensors AGRO PLUS has the exact same features and workflow of N3tSensors AGRO with the additional integration, upstream, of the Hawk-Eye™ Systems.
